Wmns Ace Summerlite 'White Light Thistle'
results.story: The Nike women’s Ace Summerlite ‘White Light Thistle’ delivers a lightweight golf shoe that places a premium on comfort. A thin and flexible overlay reinforces a breathable white mesh upper tuned to the contours of the female foot, complete with a shallow toe box, tapered heel and a higher arch. Both the tongue and collar are lined in micro-suede to allow for barefoot wear. A plush foam midsole is undergirded by a rubber outsole with an integrated traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: Wmns Flex Experience Run 10 'White Violet Shock'
Wmns Gel Venture 8 'Carrier Grey Red Brick'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Venture 8 ‘Carrier Grey Red Brick’ features a durable lugged rubber outsole designed for running in the great outdoors. A black EVA midsole yields soft cushioning and a smooth ride, while a purple TPU shank plate delivers midfoot stability. Up top, breathable grey mesh is reinforced with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with black and red tiger stripes. Webbing straps integrated into the lacing system provides a feeling of lockdown.

results.name: Wmns Gel Venture 8 'Black Sheet Rock'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Venture 8 ‘Black Sheet Rock’ highlights subtle pop of color on a running shoe designed for outdoor trails. The sneaker makes use of breathable black and white mesh throughout the upper, featuring a more accommodating toe box that allows for toe splay. Bright aqua accents land on webbing straps integrated into the lacing system, as well as a TPU shank in the lugged rubber outsole. Lightweight cushioning is provided by an EVA midsole with ASICS’ Gel technology in the heel.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Hierro v6 'Black Fig'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam Hierro v6 ‘Black Fig’ showcases muted earth tones on a rugged trail runner built to take on the elements. TPU threads are woven into the brown mesh upper for added support and protection in high-wear areas, while laser perforations deliver improved breathability. The lightweight build is mounted on a textured Fresh Foam midsole, reinforced underfoot by a lugged Vibram outsole for multi-directional traction.

results.name: Wmns Suede Classic 'International Women's Day'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Suede Classic ‘International Women’s Day’ celebrates the annual observance with a monochromatic pastel design. A soft lavender hue saturates the soft suede upper, accented with a tonal Formstrip and silver foil PUMA Suede branding on the lateral side panel. Mismatched lace jewels display PUMA’s jumping cat logo and ‘Girl Power’ script. A durable rubber cupsole, complete with distinctively textured sidewalls, maintains the sneaker’s one-note finish.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'Broderie'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Broderie’ gives the foundational sneaker a lifted look, courtesy of an exaggerated EVA midsole with traditional license-plate branding and contrasting black pinstripes. The stacked tooling is underpinned by a standard brown rubber outsole with a customary diamond tread. Up top, cream-hued canvas is entirely covered in embroidered florals for a spring-ready look.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'White Ivory Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘White Ivory Blue’ pairs classic tennis style with a modern, sustainable build. The white synthetic leather upper is made with 50% recycled content and features familiar perforated three-stripe branding on the side panels. An adidas Trefoil is stamped on the pale blue heel tab, while a contrasting beige tongue is marked with the iconic Stam Smith logo. The low-top rides on a durable rubber cupsole that’s unchanged from the original.

results.name: Wmns SL Andridge 'Glow Pink'
results.story: The adidas women’s SL Andridge ‘Glow Pink’ delivers a subtle colorway of a lifestyle silhouette that borrows liberally from ‘70s running shoes. Ghillie-style lacing secures an upper crafted from beige textile with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Matching leather three-stripes are enlivened with exposed zigzag stitching. The sneaker rides on an exaggerated midsole in a blend of EVA and TPU, supported underfoot by a pink-hued rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Stan Smith 'Halo Ivory'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Halo Ivory’ updates the iconic silhouette with a tan synthetic leather upper made with 50% recycled content. The sustainable build comes replete with signature Stan Smith details, including tonal stitching, perforated three-stripes and a Trefoil logo stamped on the heel tab. adidas’ Primegreen branding adorns the sockliner, indicating that the shoe contains zero virgin plastic. A standard white rubber cupsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Broderie'
results.story: Inspired by boho crochet fashion, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Broderie’ wears a cream-hued canvas upper entirely covered in embroidered florals. The subtle texture is accompanied by standard Chuck details, including a rubber toe cap, chrome eyelets and a circular All Star ankle patch. The high-top is mounted on a platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. Black pinstripes and a Converse license plate add recognizable elements to the sneaker’s revamped tooling.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Platform Low 'Black Leopard'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low ‘Black Leopard’ gives the classic silhouette a fashion-forward look. The low-top is clad in black canvas with leopard-print detailing on the laces and heel overlay. Standard Chuck tooling is replaced by an elevated platform midsole with soft EVA cushioning. The raised sidewall is accented with traditional black pinstripes and a Converse license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a brown rubber outsole features a customary diamond tread for durable traction.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Cloud Pink'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Cloud Pink’ brings back the OG Speedcat, released in 1981 and inspired by F1 track style. The sneaker’s low-profile pink suede upper is reinforced with a tonal T-toe overlay and accented with a white suede Formstrip. Additional branding hits include PUMA’s jumping cat logo on the lateral toe and heel tab. Underfoot, the black rubber outsole continues the motorsport theme with a herringbone tire tread and rounded driver’s heel.

results.name: Wmns Speedcat LS 'Black White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Speedcat LS ‘Black White’ delivers a simple two-tone colorway of a low-profile silhouette inspired by F1 racing. The streamlined upper is outfitted in black suede with a tonal T-toe overlay and a contrasting white suede Formstrip. Jumping cat branding lands on the heel tab and lateral toe, while a gold-foil PUMA No. 1 Logo is stamped on the quarter panel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a distinctive tire tread and a rounded driver’s heel for added traction.

results.name: Wmns Deviate Nitro Elite 'White Lava Blast'
results.story: The PUMA Deviate Nitro Elite ‘White Lava Blast’ features a lightweight build engineered for speed. An off-white finish is applied to the semi-translucent mono mesh upper, accented with a black and red PUMA Formstrip and reflective silver detailing that wraps around the deconstructed collar. A responsive NITRO ELITE foam midsole is supported by a carbon fiber INNOPLATE that generates improved energy transfer at toe-off. Underfoot, a PUMAGRIP LT rubber outsole is good for lasting multi-surface traction.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Storm Wind Pure Silver'
results.story: Releasing as part of a ‘Washed Florals’ pack, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Storm Wind Pure Silver’ opens up the heel and transforms the low-top into a stylish slip-on. Traditional laces secure the dark brown canvas upper, enlivened with metallic silver binding on the tongue, collar and throat. The sneaker’s interior lining is rendered in a hot pink finish, complemented by watercolor florals on the custom sockliner.

results.name: Nike Crater Impact Summit White Green Glow (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White’ pairs a pastel palette with efficient construction designed to reduce manufacturing waste. The latter is achieved through the application of an embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays on a minimalist mesh upper. Plush cushioning arrives via a lifted Crater foam midsole built with 12% recycled content. Underfoot, the outsole features durable rubber in high-wear areas made with 15% Nike Grind.

results.name: Wmns Classic Nylon SP 'Energy Glow'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Classic Nylon SP ‘Energy Glow’ applies a fluorescent finish to a modernized take on the 1984 original. Stretch nylon is utilized on the upper, fortified with no-sew skins and a midfoot and heel overlay made with synthetic suede. The airy build is mounted on a plush EVA midsole, which works in tandem with a removable EVA sockliner for an ultra-cushioned ride. Underfoot, gum rubber is placed in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Pink Quartz'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Pink Quartz’ reinterprets the classic sneaker as a summer-ready espadrille. The standard rubber midsole is elevated and covered in braided textile, while the canvas upper is updated with a soft pastel hue and frayed detailing. Chrome eyelets and a Converse All Star tongue tag maintain the classic Chuck Taylor look and feel. Underfoot, a traditional diamond-tread rubber outsole delivers reliable grip.

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Oslo Maja 'Ultramarine American Beauty'
results.story: Inspired by the British artist’s ‘one line-drawings,’ the Mr. Doodle x PUMA women’s Oslo Maja ‘Ultramarine American Beauty’ features an all-over graphic formed with one continuous line. The doodle-like illustration covers a canvas upper in mismatched blue and red finishes. Asymmetric color blocking continues on the chenille Formstrip, rendered in orange and yellow on the lateral and medial side. Mr. Doodle branding appears on the tongue tag, while his illustrated characters adorn each heel tab. A platform EVA midsole anchors the low-top.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'Washed Florals - Egret'
results.story: Launching as part of a ‘Washed Florals’ collection, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High ‘Egret’ updates the iconic sneaker with elevated tooling and spring-ready details. An off-white finish is applied to the recycled poly-canvas upper, featuring a washed-out floral print on the binding that lines the collar and throat. The faded florals are repeated on the circular Chuck Taylor patch that adorns medial ankle. A raised platform midsole packs soft EVA cushioning for a improved comfort.

results.name: Mr. Doodle x Wmns Cruise Rider 'Eggnog Ultramarine'
results.story: The Mr. Doodle x PUMA women’s Cruise Rider ‘Eggnog Ultramarine’ draws inspiration from the British artist’s ‘one-line drawings,’ featuring illustrations formed with one long continuous line. The sneaker makes use of a cream-colored textile upper with contrasting red suede overlays at the toe and heel. On the lateral side, a bird doodle is embroidered atop a blue leather Formstrip. Mr. Doodle branding makes its way to the woven tongue tag and exaggerated foam midsole.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Low 'Color Espadrille - Banana Cake'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Low ‘Banana Cake’ transforms the classic silhouette into a summer-ready espadrille, highlighted by an EVA midsole with braided-textile sidewalls. Up top, the yellow canvas build is decorated with frayed foxing that enhances the shoe’s breezy aesthetic. Additional details include a tonal canvas toe cap, chrome eyelets and a standard Converse All Star tag atop the tongue. A traditional Chuck Taylor outsole in brown rubber provides durable traction.

results.name: Wmns EvoRide 2 'Black White'
results.story: The ASICS women’s EvoRide 2 ‘Black White’ presents an elemental two-tone colorway of a lightweight silhouette built for daily runs. The black engineered mesh upper is made with 20% recycled materials and designed to keep feet cool. The supportive feel of the FlyteFoam midsole is enhanced with GuideSole technology, featuring pronounced toe-spring that generates forward propulsion and increased efficiency. Underfoot, the Aharplus outsole places durable rubber in high-wear areas for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Football Grey'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Football Grey’ highlights neon accents on a tracik-inspired silhouette that channels the brand’s sustainability efforts. 100% recycled polyester laces secure a light grey mesh upper, accented with an embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays that yield efficient manufacturing and scrap waste reduction. 12% recycled content makes up the composition of the speckled Crater foam midsole, supported underfoot by durable rubber made in part with Nike Grind.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule 'Washed Florals - Egret Light Gold'
results.story: Drawn from the ‘Washed Florals’ collection, the Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Dainty Mule ‘Egret Light Gold’ converts the sneaker icon into a convenient slip-on. An off-white canvas upper is trimmed in metallic bronze and secured with traditional lace closure. Converse branding lands on the Ortholite sockliner, featuring a washed-out pink and green floral print. Underfoot, a standard Chuck Taylor rubber outsole comes complete with a familiar diamond traction pattern.

results.name: Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Carrier Grey Light Blue'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Carrier Grey Light Blue’ features dual-layer mesh construction that yields an intricate all-over design throughout the seamless upper. Made with 20% recycled content, the lightweight build is secured with flat laces that incorporate reflective threads for increased visibility in low-light conditions. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a FlyteFoam midsole with ASICS Gel cushioning in the heel for enhanced impact protection.

results.name: Wmns Crater Impact 'Summit White Grey Fog'
results.story: The Nike women’s Crater Impact ‘Summit White Grey Fog’ highlights isolated pops of color on a track-inspired silhouette made with sustainability in mind. Speckled detailing on the bulky midsole indicates Crater Foam, composed of a blend of recycled Nike Grind and standard foam materials. Up top, the off-white mesh build is enlivened with orange zigzag stitching and a webbing pull tab in the same vibrant hue. An embroidered Swoosh and straight-edged overlays contribute to the sneaker’s efficient build.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue Wide 'White Cloud Pink'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue Wide ‘White Cloud Pink’ highlights pastel hues on a lightweight, minimalist runner that provides sock-like comfort and a smooth ride. The breathable textile knit upper is secured with laces that are integrated into a supportive midfoot saddle, constructed from synthetic leather and decorated with signature ‘N’ branding. A cushy Fresh Foam midsole is reinforced underfoot by a grippy gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue 'White Cloud Pink'
results.story: The New Balance women’s Fresh Foam Cruzv1 Reissue ‘White Cloud Pink’ delivers a sock-like running shoe that pairs an airy build with a pastel color palette. A webbing pull tab at the heel allows easy entry into an engineered knit upper, reinforced with a molded Foam Comfort Heel and a synthetic leather midfoot cage stamped with New Balance’s ‘N’ logo. The slip-on construction is mounted on a Fresh Foam midsole that yields plush cushioning with each step.

Wmns UltraBoost 4.0 DNA 'White Cream'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 4.0 DNA ‘White Cream’ utilizes a Primeknit upper in a subtle blend of tan and cream fibers. The breathable knit build, made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic and lined in comfortable textile, rests on a full-length Boost midsole in a pristine white finish. Branding hits include a discreet adidas tongue tag and ‘UltraBoost’ embossed on the molded heel counter. Underfoot, a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole delivers optimal grip.

Collina Strada x Wmns Classic Leather Legacy 'Call Mom'
results.story: Launching as part of a capsule collection with Hillary Taymour’s fashion brand, the Collina Strada x Reebok women’s Classic Leather Legacy ‘Call Mom’ features a sustainable build covered in brushstroke detailing. 40% recycled vegan leather is utilized on the upper, secured with laces and lined in textile made with 100% recycled polyester. A woven tag on the lateral eyestay displays Collina branding, while ‘Call Mom’ is inscribed across the heel tabs of the left and right shoe. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a plush EVA midsole.
